'''醛糖1-脱氢酶 (NAD<sup>+</sup>)'''（{{lang-en|aldose 1-dehydrogenase (NAD<sup>+</sup>)}}，[[EC编号|EC]] [http://enzyme.expasy.org/EC/1.1.1.121 1.1.1.121]），是一种以[[烟酰胺腺嘌呤二核苷酸|NAD<sup>+</sup>]]或[[烟酰胺腺嘌呤二核苷酸磷酸|NADP<sup>+</sup>]]为[[受体_(生物化学)|受体]]，其作用于[[供体|供体]][[次甲基|CH]]-[[羟基|OH]][[基团|基团]]上的[[氧化还原酶|氧化还原酶]]。这种[[酶|酶]]能[[催化|催化]]以下[[酶促反应|酶促反应]]：

:[[D-醛糖|<small>D</small>-醛糖]] + [[烟酰胺腺嘌呤二核苷酸|NAD<sup>+</sup>]] <math>\rightleftharpoons</math> [[醛糖酸内酯|<small>D</small>-醛糖酸内酯]] + NADH + [[氢离子|H<sup>+</sup>]]

醛糖1-脱氢酶 (NAD<sup>+</sup>)也能催化[[D-葡萄糖|<small>D</small>-葡萄糖]]、2-脱氧-<small>D</small>-葡萄糖、6-脱氧-<small>D</small>-葡萄糖、[[D-半乳糖|<small>D</small>-半乳糖]]、6-脱氧-<small>D</small>-半乳糖、2-脱氧-<small>L</small>-阿拉伯糖以及[[D-木糖|<small>D</small>-木糖]]等发生反应，并会受到[[1,10-邻氮二菲|1,10-邻氮二菲]]、[[2,3-苯并呋喃|2,3-苯并呋喃]]、[[己二烯雌二醇|己二烯雌二醇]]、[[吲唑|吲唑]]、[[吲哚|吲哚]]等[[有机分子|有机分子]]及[[银离子|Ag<sup>+</sup>]]、[[钙离子|Ca<sup>2+</sup>]]等[[阳离子|阳离子]]的抑制。<ref>{{cite journal | author = Asada Y, Endo S, Inoue Y, Mamiya H, Hara A, Kunishima N, Matsunaga T | date = 2009 | title = Biochemical and structural characterization of a short-chain dehydrogenase/reductase of ''Thermus thermophilus'' HB8: a hyperthermostable aldose-1-dehydrogenase with broad substrate specificity. | journal = Chem. Biol. Interact | volume = 178 | pages = 117-126 | pmid = 18926808 | issue = 1-3 | url = http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/18926808}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | author = Dahms AS, Anderson RL | date = 1972 | title = <small>D</small>-Fucose metabolism in a pseudomonad. I. Oxidation of <small>D</small>-fucose to <small>D</small>-fucono- -lactone by a <small>D</small>-aldohexose dehydrogenase | journal = J. Biol. Chem. | volume = 247 | pages = 2222-2227 | pmid = 4335867 | issue = 7 | url = http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/4335867}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | author = Nishiya Y, Tamura N, Tamura T | date = 2004 | title = Analysis of bacterial glucose dehydrogenase homologs from thermoacidophilic archaeon ''Thermoplasma acidophilum'': finding and characterization of aldohexose dehydrogenase | journal = Biosci Biotechnol Biochem. | volume = 68 | pages = 2451-2456 | pmid = 4335867 | issue = 12 | url = http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/15618614 | access-date = 2013-07-12 | archive-date = 2019-06-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190614081129/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/15618614 | dead-url = no }}</ref>

